OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man shot
OL,4,Cin chest by Gwent Police
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) has launched an
OL,8,Finvestigation after a 21-year-old man
OL,9,Fwas shot and seriously injured by
OL,10,FGwent Police.
OL,12,FOn 10 July 2026, an emergency call was
OL,13,Fmade to police by a man who said he
OL,14,Fwas armed with a crossbow. The man
OL,15,Falso made threats to harm himself and
OL,16,Fothers.
OL,18,FIn the early hours the following day,
OL,19,Fpolice arrived at the scene in Newport
OL,20,Fand found the man inside a property,
OL,21,Fholding a crossbow.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
