FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784305119
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man shot
OL,4,Cin chest by Gwent Police
OL,6,FAccording to the IOPC, it has
OL,7,Fconfirmed that negotiations between
OL,8,Fpolice and the man broke down and the
OL,9,Fman faced officers with the crossbow
OL,10,Fraised.
OL,12,FIt said that one of the officers
OL,13,Fdischarged a single shot during the
OL,14,Fincident, striking the man in his
OL,15,Fchest.
OL,17,FThe man received first aid and an
OL,18,Fambulance then transported him to the
OL,19,Fhospital, where he remains in a stable
OL,20,Fcondition.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
