PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784305119
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man shot
OL,4,Cin chest by Gwent Police
OL,6,FHis injuries are no longer considered
OL,7,Flife-threatening following an
OL,8,Femergency surgery whilst in hospital.
OL,10,FThe IOPC declared an independent
OL,11,Finvestigation after Gwent Police
OL,12,Freferred the incident to them on 11
OL,13,FJuly 2026.
OL,15,FAccording to the organisation, it has
OL,16,Fsecured a police firearm for
OL,17,Fexamination and it has also reviewed
OL,18,Fbody-worn camera footage, alongside
OL,19,FCCTV.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
