OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man shot
OL,4,Cin chest by Gwent Police
OL,6,FIOPC Director of Engagement, Derrick
OL,7,FCampbell said: "The use of firearms by
OL,8,Fpolice officers is rare but where
OL,9,Fpotentially lethal force has been
OL,10,Fused, it is important that we carry
OL,11,Fout an independent investigation into
OL,12,Fthe circumstances."
OL,26,@oD@POU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
