PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784305119
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man shot
OL,4,Cin chest by Gwent Police
OL,6,FMr Campbell continued: "We can confirm
OL,7,Fat this stage that all the officers
OL,8,Finvolved in the operation, including
OL,9,Fthe firearms officer who discharged
OL,10,Ftheir weapon, are being treated as
OL,11,Fwitnesses because there is no
OL,12,Findication they may have breached
OL,13,Fpolice professional standards or
OL,14,Fcommitted a criminal offence.
OL,26,@nD@XOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
