PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784305119
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man shot
OL,4,Cin chest by Gwent Police
OL,6,F"We are in the initial phase of our
OL,7,Finvestigation which is looking at the
OL,8,Fplanning and execution of the firearms
OL,9,Fdeployment, the actions and decisions
OL,10,Fof officers and staff, including the
OL,11,Fdischarge of a police firearm and
OL,12,Fwhether any use of force was
OL,13,Freasonable, necessary and
OL,14,Fproportionate. We are also
OL,15,Finvestigating the aftercare provided
OL,16,Fto the man by police officers".
OL,26,@nD@AOU
